Model Micro Paragraphs
â€¢	Intro one liner: â€œPlaintiff seeks a narrowly tailored order compelling [X] because [Rule/Statute] requires [Y] on this record at ECF [##], [date].â€
â€¢	Element line: â€œElement 2 (causation) is met because [dated fact + exhibit], which [defendant] does not rebut (ECF [##]).â€

